 <span data-ttu-id="af459-228">时间将默认为 UTC。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="af459-228">The time will default to UTC.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="af459-229">如果你想要在本地时间指定的时间，然后指定<xref:System.DateTime.Kind%2A>属性`time`对象作为<xref:System.DateTimeKind.Local?displayProperty=nameWithType>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="af459-229">If you want to specify the time in local time, then specify the <xref:System.DateTime.Kind%2A> property of the `time` object as <xref:System.DateTimeKind.Local?displayProperty=nameWithType>.</span></span>  



## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="af459-230">下面的代码连接到托管服务器端口号"5000。"上的"adamHost1.fabrikam.com"ADAM 实例</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="af459-230">The following code connects to the ADAM instance hosted by the server "adamHost1.fabrikam.com" on port number "5000."</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="af459-231">中指定的用户名 (adamAdmin) 和密码 (SecretPwd123)<xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalContext>构造函数。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="af459-231">The username (adamAdmin), and password (SecretPwd123) are specified in the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalContext> constructor.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="af459-232">将为容器下的所有 authenticable 主体执行搜索"DC = adamApp1，DC = fabrikam，DC = com"不登录到此 ADAM 实例最近 45 天内。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="af459-232">A search is performed for all authenticable principals under the container "DC=adamApp1,DC=fabrikam,DC=com" that have not logged on to this ADAM instance for the last 45 days.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="af459-233">然后删除搜索返回的主体。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="af459-233">The principals returned by the search are then deleted.</span></span>  

```  
PrincipalContext ctx = new PrincipalContext(  
                                      ContextType.ApplicationDirectory,   
                                      "adamHost1.fabrikam.com:5000",   
                                      "DC=adamApp1,DC=fabrikam,DC=com",   
                                      "adamAdmin", "SecretPwd123");  

PrincipalSearchResult<AuthenticablePrincipal> oldPrincipals =   
                     AuthenticablePrincipal.FindByLogonTime(ctx,   
                            (DateTime.Now - new TimeSpan(45, 0, 0, 0)),   
                            MatchType.LessThan);  

foreach (Principal p in oldPrincipals)  
{  
    p.Delete();  
}  

oldPrincipals.Dispose();  
ctx.Dispose();  

```

